, CoH clerics, reapply DS, nuke (depending on where you are raiding), mala.  Seems pretty useful to me.  There aren't any pathing issues with this tactic, other than the path the pet takes back to its guard spot, which doesn't matter cause its not KoS anyways.  Also, I think most people 50+ realize that earth pets aren't what you want for raids, and even if you did use one it wouldn't matter much, for most high level raids the mobs' MR is high enough that they'd resist the root anyways. <p>~~
