Epic pets doing as much damage as a 60 warrior?  Against what?  Regular exp mob maybe, but not against high level encounters.  The Epic pet is only slightly better in terms of melee than the regular pets.  If the pet isn't winning taunt (which it won't in a raid), than the DS is useless.  The max hits will be higher than a regular pet, but it still misses a ton.  Overall it probably does 10-20% more damage, but we're talking about relatively small damage amounts compared to warriors, monks, rogues.<br>
<br>
I'll try to get a log, problem is on real raids there is so much battle spam it lags most people out. <p>AbMagFab baFgaMbA<BR>
